\c 28 
\m \bd Faarfannaa \bd*\bd 28\bd*
\s2 \bdit \zbr\bdit*Waammanni Gargaarsaa Dhaga'amee Galanni Dhi'eeffamuu (Kan Daawit)
\m \bd 1\bd* Yaa Waaqayyo, si kattaa jabaa kootti nan iyyadha, ati ana jalaa hin didin! Akka warra boollatti gad bu'anii akka ani hin taanetti, ati ana jalaa calluma hin jedhin.
\m \bd 2\bd* Harka koo mana qulqullummaa kee keessaa gara iddoo isa hundumaa irra caalaa qulqulluutti, yeroon ol kaafadhu sagalee himata koo isa ani gargaarsaaf sitti iyyadhu, anaaf dhaga'i!
\m \bd 3\bd* Warra jal'ootaa wajjin, warra hamaa godhanii wajjinis ana hin butin! Isaan garaa isaaniitti hamaa in yaadu, afaaniin immoo nagaa namatti in dubbatu.
\m \bd 4\bd* Ati akka hojii isaaniitti, akka gocha isaanii isa hamaatti isaaniif kenni! Akka hojii harka isaaniitti isaaniif kenni, amala isaan argisiisaniif waan ta'u isaanitti deebisi!
\m \bd 5\bd* Isaan gocha Waaqayyoo yookiis isa harki isaa hojjete waan hin ilaalleef, inni isaan in diiga malee, deebi'ee isaan hin ijaaru.
\m \bd 6\bd* Sagalee himata kootii waan anaaf dhaga'eef, Waaqayyoon nan jajadha.
\m \bd 7\bd* Waaqayyo aangoo koo ti, gaachana koo tis, garaan koo isa in amanata; ani gargaarsa argadheera, kanaafis garaan koo in ililcha; faarfannaa kootiinis galata isaaf nan galcha.
\m \bd 8\bd* Waaqayyo aangoo saba isaatii ti, isa ofii dibee moosiseefis gargaarsaa fi da'oo dha.
\m \bd 9\bd* Ati saba kee oolchi, warra kan keetiis eebbisi! Bara baraan tiksee isaanii ta'iif, ol fuudhii isaan baadhus!
\b 
